# Quality Bar

- Code compiles and passes linters/type checks.
- Tests run locally; CI is green.
- No unrelated files changed.
- No mocks/stubs in dev/prod code paths.
- No secret or `.env` changes without explicit approval.
- Clear naming, short functions, cohesive modules.
- Public API changes documented and versioned (if applicable).
